<scriptment id="39000" point="group_demo2" localizationstatus="original" fictionaldate="2011-07-24" status="final">
	<part>
		<narration>The accomplice from The Group's second demonstration delivers his informal apology. Yuki isn't really paying attention.</narration>
		<line id="1000" speaker="miyamoto" voicelang="ja">My apologies, Mademoiselle Soleil.</line>
		<line id="2000" speaker="miyamoto" voicelang="ja">Both Iwata and I felt that demonstration was crass,</line>
		<line id="3000" speaker="miyamoto" voicelang="ja">especially in the midst of a recession.</line>
		<line id="4000" speaker="miyamoto" voicelang="ja">I think I'm done with The Group.</line>
		<line id="5000" speaker="miyamoto" voicelang="ja">I'm gonna leave Tokyo for a while.</ilne>
	</part>
</scriptment>